---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="North Carolina Case Study | Upfront" description="See how North Carolina built a unified statewide ECE data system with Upfront, connecting 100 counties with real-time capacity visibility.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal hover:text-brand-teal/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        North Carolina
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-gray">
        Building a Unified Statewide ECE Data System
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-orange uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Challenge
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        The Problem
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        North Carolina's early childhood education system spans 100 counties, multiple state agencies, and thousands of providers. Managing this complex ecosystem presented significant challenges:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Siloed systems: licensing, subsidy, and quality data lived in separate databases with no integration</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Manual reporting: county-level staff spent days compiling reports that were outdated by the time they reached leadership</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Inconsistent data: provider information varied between systems, making accurate analysis impossible</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Limited visibility: state leaders couldn't see real-time childcare capacity or demand</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Solution -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Solution
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        A Unified Statewide Data Platform
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-8">
        Upfront partnered with North Carolina to build a comprehensive data platform that connects all 100 counties and provides real-time visibility into the state's ECE landscape.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Unified Provider Records</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Single source of truth linking licensing, quality ratings, and subsidy participation across all providers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Automated Data Pipelines</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Nightly syncs from state systems eliminate manual data entry and ensure information is always current.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Interactive Dashboards</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Real-time visibility into capacity, waitlists, and funding allocation by county.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Provider Self-Service</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Programs update their information directly, improving data accuracy and reducing administrative burden.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Configurable Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Automated reports for state and federal compliance requirements, saving countless hours of manual work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Results -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
          The Results
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
          Statewide Transformation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Upfront's unified platform has transformed how North Carolina manages and understands its early childhood education landscape.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">100</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            counties with unified data in a single platform
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">90%</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            reduction in reporting time for county staff
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">Real-time</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            capacity visibility statewide
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
